Source code for the post
http://matcross.wordpress.com/2013/07/15/jenkins-comes-to-nag/
showing a Jenkins backup script inspired by
http://jenkins-ci.org/content/keeping-your-configuration-and-data-subversion

backup.csh
  the script.
  This takes one optional command-line argument: the commit message to use if
  there are changes in the working copy.
